      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom condition, having been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior finish retains its deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with zero chips, swirls, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin remains indistinguishable from the day it left the factory; the premium leather surfaces are supple and free of any creases, while the carpets have been shielded by original protective liners. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive binder of records included. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road wear or weather exposure. Riding on pristine alloy wheels with brand-new performance tires, this is a turn-key opportunity for the most discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection. Non-smoker, no pets, and always hand-washed.",
